### VS Code REST Client Config
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. 模拟 Pull 操作 (获取增量数据)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sync/pull
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lastSyncCursor": 0
}

### 2. 模拟 Push 操作 (上传新小说)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sync/push
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lastSyncCursor": 1700000000000,
    "changes": {
        "novels": [
            {
                "id": "test-novel-1",
                "title": "测试小说",
                "description": "这是一个通过 HTTP Client 创建的测试小说",
                "updatedAt": "2024-01-01T12:00:00"
            }
        ],
        "chapters": []
    }
}
